"12 ounces refrigerated fresh pizza dough","2 teaspoons extra-virgin olive oil","6  garlic cloves, crushed","2/3 cup fat-free ricotta cheese","2 tablespoons canola mayonnaise","2 teaspoons chopped fresh thyme","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1.5 ounces Parmigiano-Reggiano cheese, finely shredded (about 1/3 cup)","3 ounces fresh mozzarella cheese, very thinly sliced","1 teaspoon fresh lemon juice","1 teaspoon balsamic vinegar","1 1/2 cups baby arugula"